1.0.1.name: wordpress/hitcounter
1.0.1.description:
THIS PLUGIN IS NO LONGER SUPPORTED. There may be a new version in the future but for now…nothing.

A simple plugin to count and display the number of visitors on your blog posts (i.e. a read count). It distinguishes between robots, registered human, and non registered humans. The data is stored in a database table by the name of 'hitcounter'.
